    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear and still retaining that new-car smell. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage with a full service history to document its care. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a truly exceptional example of this model that needs absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 48500.0,
